{"TopicId":97206,"ForumId":66,"TopicTitle":"Modding Mondays: Blast Awesomeness Modifier","CreatedByName":"SQUAD","CreatedById":66485,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-01-19T23:40:01Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"SQUAD","CreatedById":66485,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-01-19T23:40:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022tumblr_inline_nify3gFmTa1rr2wit.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022https://31.media.tumblr.com/f877983c4f5dc185bb3b4a0e8611b711/tumblr_inline_nify3gFmTa1rr2wit.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/_O34_lwsMGo?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhether you like big BAMs or little BAMs, \u003Cstrong\u003Emarce\u003C/strong\u003E\u0027s\u00A0\u003Cspan\u003E \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/103114-0-90-Blast-Awesomeness-Modifier-%28BAM%29-v1-1-1-2015-01-01\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EBLAST AWESOMENESS MODIFIER\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E attributes a more appropriate explosion to different sized parts. As marce puts it, \u201CA small fuel tank will explode a little, a big one will explode a lot.\u201D\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGet more info and download \u003Cstrong\u003EBlast Awesomeness Modifier\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/103114-0-90-Blast-Awesomeness-Modifier-%28BAM%29-v1-1-1-2015-01-01\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E HERE\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E \u003C/span\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"iFlyAllTheTime","CreatedById":111190,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-01-20T00:00:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EInteresting!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Starwhip","CreatedById":83990,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-01-20T00:18:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EAlready have it. Very cool.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"marce","CreatedById":110351,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-01-20T00:25:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EWooo, thanks once again SQUAD! \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_embarrassed.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:blush:\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI\u0027d like to point out, that it\u0027s less dependant on the size of a part than on the amount (every unit counts) and type (fuel increases, water decreases explosiveness) of the contained resources: Empty orange tank has low BAM, full one has a lot of BAM. \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EOf course, bigger parts can contain more fuel and therefore explode a lot.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E@Starwhip: glad you like it!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Sirrobert","CreatedById":70591,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-01-20T21:23:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EInteresting. I\u0027ll be trying this out for sure\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"BudgetHedgehog\uFEFF","CreatedById":104112,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-01-21T01:04:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ELove this little mod, helps immersion a lot. Always seemed weird that structural girders exploded with the same intensity as a full Kerbodyne tank. Also, love that the name plays on the stock log report when things explode. Thanks to marce (again) for an awesome mod!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Whirligig Girl","CreatedById":36077,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-01-21T02:08:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EBump to get rid of fake devnotes.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Starwhip","CreatedById":83990,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-01-21T02:10:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022GregroxMun\u0022 data-cite=\u0022GregroxMun\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EBump to get rid of fake devnotes.\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI is sorry. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}